# Supplies the information required to perform a mosaic 
# exposure sequence.
# Module code: 692500
#
# Example: TELMOSAIC 35.0 CB 2 3 3 240.0 240.0 10.0
#
%double;rotation;0 to 2*PI;tangent plane rotation.
%InstrumentConfig;config;a valid config for the CCD camera;camera configuration
%int;xCount;1 - 5;number of cells in rotated X direction.
%int;yCount;1 - 5;number of cells in rotated Y direction.
%double;xOffset;0 - 3600 arcsec;offset in rotated X direction.
%double;yOffset;0 - 3600 arcsec;offset in rotated Y direction.
%int;exposure; 0 < exposure < 7200000;exposure (millis).
